snippet.title: Gears + Millstone
snippet.description:
Gears are attached to axle bearings by right-clicking, and removed by shift clicking. The number of teeth on adjacent gears determines the change in speed.

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/dunkleosteus
Download Here: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/terrafirmacraftplus
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TFC_Dunk

Discord: https://discord.gg/E6gBbxf



TFC+ Wiki: https://plus.terrafirmacraft.com/Main_Page
